Example: American Roulette

Net gain while betting on red on a roulette spin.




If we bet a dollar on red, then our net gain is
\[
\text{gain} = \begin{cases}
+1 & \text{with prob } \frac{18}{38} \\
-1 & \text{with prob } \frac{20}{38}
\end{cases}
\]
